Class Transition

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.graphicsutilities.transition.Transition

  • public class Transition
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates transitions between images. Note: Images to be transitioned between must be of the same resolution. No scaling is implemented here.
